#. REF: pts1ed1.177, pts2ed1.381, sc13
msgctxt "sn7.14:13.1"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ brāhmaṇamahāsālaṃ puttā gharaṃ netvā nhāpetvā paccekaṃ dussayugena acchādesuṃ. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin’s sons led him back home, bathed him, and each clothed him with a fine pair of garments. "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.2"
msgid "Atha kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo ekaṃ dussayugaṃ ādāya yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin, taking one pair of garments, went to the Buddha and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.14:13.4"
msgid "“mayaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā nāma ācariyassa ācariyadhanaṃ pariyesāma. "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, we brahmins seek a fee for our teacher. "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.5"
msgid "Paṭiggaṇhatu me bhavaṃ gotamo ācariyadhanan”ti. "
msgstr "May Master Gotama please accept my teacher’s fee!” "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.6"
msgid "Paṭiggahesi bhagavā anukampaṃ upādāya. "
msgstr "So the Buddha accepted it out of compassion. "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.7"
msgid "Atha kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the well-to-do brahmin said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.8"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama … "

msgctxt "sn7.14:13.9"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"

